public interface IFluentCollectionProperty<Owner,Value,Container extends Collection<Value>>
extends IFluentProperty<Owner,Container>

The aim of IFluentCollectionProperty interface is to unify FluentCollectionProperty and FluentCollectionDelegateProperty classes into one hierarchy.
